Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Thank you Barry. Keep up the great work. We must WIN the wonderful Commonwealth of Pennsylvania. Comrade Kamala has always been strongly against Fracking, and that will never change — no matter what she is all of a sudden saying now. Fracking under Kamala is DEAD, and so is everything else, including our once great Country!!! DJT
